Requirements 

 Bachelor’s degree in computer science, information technology, or a similar field; 
 HTML/CSS: Proficiency in HTML5 and CSS3 is fundamental. Candidates should be adept at creating responsive and accessible web interfaces; 
 JavaScript: Solid understanding of JavaScript, including ES6+ features, is essential. Familiarity with frameworks or libraries such as React.js, Angular, or Vue.js is often preferred; 
 Version Control: Experience with Git or other version control systems is commonly required; 
 Responsive Design: Ability to implement responsive design principles to ensure applications function seamlessly across various devices and screen sizes; 
 UI/UX: Ability to translate designs from Figma, Adobe XD, or similar tools into functional interfaces; 
 Testing and Debugging: Competence in testing and debugging code to maintain high-quality standards; 
 Basic Back-End Understanding: While primarily focused on front-end development, a basic understanding of back-end processes can be advantageous for integrating APIs into frontend applications; 
 Familiar with CI/CD tooling and infrastructure (Jenkins) is a plus; 
 Familiar with virtualization, containerization, and orchestration technologies (Docker, Kubernetes) is a plus. 

 Responsibilities 

 Develop and maintain frontend applications (web/mobile); 
 Collaborate with cross-functional teams (i.e., Product Solution Architect, Business Analyst, Data Engineering, and QA) on project and product planning and execution; 
 Optimize application performance and usability; 
 Ensure code quality through reviews and testing; 
 Work with third-party dependencies and APIs; 
 Stay updated with the latest trends and technologies in frontend development.

Java Development Engineer Recruitment Requirements : 

 1. Bachelor's degree or above in Computer Science or related field, with 2-3 years of development experience; 
 2. Front-end technologies: Familiar with Vue (2/3) framework, proficient in Vue component usage, HTML, JavaScript (ES6+), and CSS3; able to independently develop backend management system pages; 
 3. Back-end technologies: Solid Java fundamentals, proficient in Spring Boot framework, able to independently develop server-side interfaces; 
 4. Database and middleware: Familiar with MySQL/PostgreSQL databases, with SQL optimization capabilities; 
 5. Familiar with Redis, understanding the use cases of caching and distributed locks; 
 6. Version control: Proficient in Git, with good collaborative development habits; 
 7. Payment industry experience: At least 1 year of experience in POS business/payment systems, familiar with payment processes, etc.; 
 8. Payment security standards: Understanding of encryption/decryption algorithms, signature verification mechanisms, certificate management, sensitive data anonymization, and other security-related knowledge; 
 9. Possesses good coding style, troubleshooting ability, and a strong sense of responsibility; highly sensitive to financial security; 
 10. Fluent in spoken  English and/or Mandarin .

Job Responsibilities 
 1. Respond to customer inquiries in a timely manner via online chat, and provide solutions to product-related and after-sales questions. 
 2. Handle customer after-sales requests, complaints and disputes, calm customer emotions, follow up on issue resolution to closure, and improve customer satisfaction. 
 3. Maintain standardized records of customer communication and feedback, organize and report regularly, and assist in optimizing service processes. 
 4. Cooperate with the team to achieve service targets and comply with the company’s customer service standards and work regulations. 
 5. Complete other tasks assigned by supervisors. 

 Job Requirements 
 - College diploma or above; 
 - Basic English communication skills, able to handle simple English inquiries and written replies; 
 - Excellent communication skills, patient and responsible, with strong service awareness and good emotional control; 
 - Able to accept shift work; 
 - Relevant customer service experience is preferred. 

 Tanggung Jawab Pekerjaan: 
 1. Menanggapi pertanyaan pelanggan secara tepat waktu melalui obrolan online, menjawab pertanyaan terkait produk dan layanan paska penjualan. 
 2. Menangani permintaan paska penjualan, keluhan dan keluhan pelanggan, menenangkan emosi pelanggan, menindaklanjuti penyelesaian masalah hingga selesai, serta meningkatkan kepuasan pelanggan. 
 3. Mencatat informasi komunikasi dan masukan balik kebutuhan pelanggan secara terstandarisasi, mengatur dan melaporkan secara berkala, serta membantu mengoptimalkan proses layanan. 
 4. Bekerja sama dengan tim untuk mencapai target layanan dan mematuhi standar layanan pelanggan serta peraturan kerja perusahaan. 
 5. Menyelesaikan tugas lain yang ditugaskan oleh atasan. 

 Kualifikasi Pekerjaan: 
 - Lulusan Diploma (D3)/ setara dan lebih tinggi; 
 - Memiliki kemampuan komunikasi Bahasa Inggris dasar, memiliki kemampuan komunikasi dan kemampuan tanya jawab sederhana dalam Bahasa Inggris; 
 - Komunikasi lancar, sabar, bertanggung jawab yang kuat dan kemampuan pengendalian emosi yang baik; 
 - Bersedia bekerja secara shift dari pagi hingga sore / dari siang hingga malam; 
 - Memiliki pengalaman atas pelayanan pelanggan (customer service/telemarketing) diutamakan
